                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== conf-sanity test 89: check tunefs --param and --erase-param{s} options ============================ 05:10:38 (1628053838)
Stopping clients: fre1135,fre1136 /mnt/lustre (opts:)
Stopping clients: fre1135,fre1136 /mnt/lustre2 (opts:)
Stopping /mnt/lustre-mgs (opts:) on fre1133
fre1133: e2label: No such file or directory while trying to open lustre-mdt1/mdt1
fre1133: Couldn&apos;t find valid filesystem superblock.
pdsh@fre1135: fre1133: ssh exited with exit code 1
tunefs --param failover.node=192.0.2.254@tcp0
fre1133: e2label: No such file or directory while trying to open lustre-mdt/mdt
fre1133: Couldn&apos;t find valid filesystem superblock.
pdsh@fre1135: fre1133: ssh exited with exit code 1
tunefs --param failover.node=192.0.2.255@tcp0
tunefs --erase-param failover.node
tunefs --erase-params
fre1133: sh: line 1: 784941 Segmentation fault      (core dumped) tunefs.lustre --erase-params lustre-mdt1/mdt1 &amp;gt; /dev/null
pdsh@fre1135: fre1133: ssh exited with exit code 139
 conf-sanity test_89: @@@@@@ FAIL: tunefs --erase-params failed 
 &lt;/pre&gt;
